Hens and pigs, yes, oh - that's another thing. We once went from - me father's - says, I want you to go - Wolsingham market with me, he said, I'm going to take a pig to the market.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15870008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 Do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7436786 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 Yes. So he says, so 
I went with him. And he puts the pig into the back of the trap there was traps in those days, he put this pig in the back of the trap and fastens the door \{ILLEGIBLE\} got - onto the seat at the front and away we went. And we were going along 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Bedburn Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, we had to go {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Bedburn Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 to go to Wolsingham you know, and - by the time we got to Wolsingham he gets out and he goes for the pig. And there was no pig. It had fallen out. And we never knew. We never heard it or anything. See, the rattle of the - trap on 
the - rough road we could hear. But however - shortly after that my sister and a boy - friend - came with their - but trap and - it - as luck would have it that they saw this pig on the roadside and they saw the marking and knew that the marking was ours.
 They have a special mark on when they go to the market. And - he picked it up, put in the tub trap and he got to Wolsingham just in time for the mart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15870008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 How fortunate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7436786 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 
It was. Yes, it was fortunate that they came behind. We were - oh, we felt awful. No pig you know, when we'd gone to the market purposely with it. We never knew how that got out. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15870008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 So you had hens and pigs then?
