\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15870008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 You used to go to the chapel things before didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7436786 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 
Yes, used to go to the chapel. But - I used to go with the old lady from West Cornforth to - if there was a social anything. That was the - that's the only thing I can remember. And there were - th
ey were very well off were these people and - they had two daughters and the youngest one and I used to go to the shows - socials. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15870008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14287592\charrsid206258 
Did you go out in the evening, you went out to a social, that's all you remember doing is it?
